snippet.title: VRSailing By BeTomorrow
snippet.description:
VR Sailing by BeTomorrow
Available for FREE on Steam:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/579050/
Running on an i7 2600 w/ gtx 980

You can't beat the price, and it is a fun (if short) diversion from yer landlubbin life... lol
